## ğŸ§© Permissions Justification  

| Permission | Purpose |
|-------------|----------|
| `activeTab` | Detects the active Gmail tab to display the Smartly Email toolbar. |
| `scripting` | Injects scripts to enable template save/insert functions within Gmail. |
| `storage` | Stores saved templates and preferences locally in the browser. |
| `https://mail.google.com/*` | Runs only on Gmail to interact with the compose window. |

Smartly Email **does not use any remote code or external resources.**

